elia]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s215/great-british-bake-off/news/a543500/jamelia-victoria-pendleton-tonights-sport-relief-bake-off-pictures.html|title=Sport Relief Bake Off \u2013 tonight's photos|date=15 January 2014|publisher=|accessdate=19 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Michael Ball (singer)|Michael Ball]]\n|-\n| [[Victoria Pendleton]]\n|-\n| rowspan=4 |4\n| rowspan=4 |[[Ed Byrne (comedian)|Ed Byrne]]\n| rowspan=4 |Pizzas\n| rowspan=4 |Eccles Cakes\n| rowspan=4 |Tiered Cakes\n| style=\"background:#d0f0c0\" | [[Alistair McGowan]]\n| rowspan=4 |{{Start date|2014|01|16|df=y}}\n| rowspan=4 |4.94\n|-\n| [[Doon Mackichan]]\n|-\n| [[Helen Skelton]]\n|-\n| [[Rochelle Humes]]\n|}\n\n=== Series 3 (2016) ===\n:{{Color box|#d0f0c0|border=darkgray}} Star Baker\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! No. !! Guest host !! Signature Challenge !! Technical Challenge !! Showstopper Challenge !! Contestants !! Airdate !! Viewers<br />(millions)\n|-\n| rowspan=4 |1\n| rowspan=4 |[[Mel Giedroyc]]\n| rowspan=4 |[[Canap\u00e9s]]\n| rowspan=4 |[[Paris\u2013Brest]]\n| rowspan=4 |Trophy Cake\n| [[David James (footballer)|David James]]\n| rowspan=4 |{{Start date|2016|01|27|df=y}}\n| rowspan=4 |6.03\n|-\n| [[Jason Manford]]\n|-\n| [[Maddy Hill]]\n|- style=\"background:#d0f0c0\"\n| [[Samantha Cameron]]\n|-\n| rowspan=4 |2\n| rowspan=4 |[[Jennifer Saunders]]\n| rowspan=4 |[[Muffin|American Muffins]]\n| rowspan=4 |[[Scotch pie|Football Pie]]\n| rowspan=4 |[[Wedding cake|Tiered Cake]]\n| [[Chris Kamara]]\n| rowspan=4 |{{Start date|2016|02|03|df=y}}\n| rowspan=4 |7.44\n|-\n| [[Ed Balls]]\n|- style=\"background:#d0f0c0\"\n| [[Kimberley Walsh]]\n|-\n| [[Victoria Coren Mitchell]]\n|-\n| rowspan=4 |3\n| rowspan=4 |[[Ed Byrne (comedian)|Ed Byrne]]\n| rowspan=4 |[[Tart|Savoury tarts]]\n| rowspan=4 |Chocolate and Beetroot Tray Bake\n| rowspan=4 |3D Biscuits\n| style=\"background:#d0f0c0\"|[[Geri Halliwell|Geri Horner]]\n| rowspan=4 |{{Start date|2016|02|1